ible, and a relatively short tail. References", "shortSummary": "The golden-chested tanager (Bangsia rothschildi) is a species of bird in the family Thraupidae. It is found in Colombia and Ecuador.", "locations": ["哥伦比亚", "厄瓜多尔"], "habitats": ["山地森林"], "lat": 4.0, "lng": -72.0, "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Bangsia_rothschildi_1897.jpg/960px-Bangsia_rothschildi_1897.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-bangsia", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-bangsia-rothschildi", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-bangsia", "species": "taxonomy-species-bangsia-rothschildi"}, "expandable": true, "x": 798.77, "y": 134.01, "z": 365.29}, {"id": "taxonomy-genus-bangsia", "name": "Bangsia", "latinName": "Bangsia", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "genus", "summary": "Bangsia（Bangsia）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联5种鸟类，如Black-and-gold tanager、Golden-chested tanager、Moss-backed tanager等5种鸟类。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 5, "x": 24.97, "y": 467.46, "z": 41.52}, {"id": "taxonomy-species-bangsia-rothschildi", "name": "Golden-chested tanager", "latinName": "Bangsia rothschildi", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "species", "summary": "Golden-chested tanager（Bangsia rothschildi）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联1种鸟类，如Golden-chested tanager。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 1, "x": 798.77, "y": 134.01, "z": 361.81}], "links": [{"key": "bird-golden-chested-tanager-b9315cd2__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-bangsia-rothschildi", "source": "bird-golden-chested-tanager-b9315cd2", "target": "taxonomy-species-bangsia-rothschildi", "relation": "belongs_to_species", "label": "属于种", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 中的种字段补充。"}, {"key": "taxonomy-species-bangsia-rothschildi__belongs_to_genus__taxonomy-genus-bangsia", "source": "taxonomy-species-bangsia-roth